Class Panel

java.lang.Object
RealEstate
Panel
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<RealEstate>, PanelInterface, PropertyInterface
public class Panel extends RealEstate implements PanelInterface
Represents a panel apartment that extends the general RealEstate class. Adds extra details such as floor level and insulation status, and modifies total price calculations accordingly.
